{"url": "https://www.tmz.com/2017/06/20/daniel-day-lewis-quits-acting/", "text": "Sir Daniel Day-Lewis -- one of the most iconic actors in the last quarter century with 3 Oscars to his name -- has reportedly quit the biz.\n\nDaniel's rep released a statement saying he will no longer be working as an actor. She added, \"He is immensely grateful to all of his collaborators and audiences over the many years. This is a private decision and neither he nor his representatives will make any further comment on this subject.\"\n\nDaniel showed immense range playing a slew of captivating roles. He won Oscars for Best Actor in \"Lincoln,\" \"My Left Foot\" and \"There Will Be Blood.\" He also earned 2 nominations for \"Gangs of New York\" and \"In the Name of the Father.\"", "images": ["https://imagez.tmz.com/image/41/o/2017/06/20/415d6114209d58d987402fb379bd1fa7_md.jpg", "https://imagez.tmz.com/image/ae/16by9/2025/11/18/aeefcdcaa57f433dbb660222c68f6031_xs.jpg", "https://static.tmz.com/tmz-web/img/thirtymilezone.svg", "https://imagez.tmz.com/image/6e/16by9/2017/03/10/6ebb77980d29527fb46e0356d215763d_xs.jpg", "https://imagez.tmz.com/image/56/16by9/2017/06/20/567a7aa968935d9fbdff35b88fd3510a_xl.jpg", "https://imagez.tmz.com/image/51/16by9/2025/11/19/5111efdc691245879252c6316ec4998f_xs.jpg", "https://imagez.tmz.com/image/35/16by9/2012/12/06/3525a0c5d7a25f66b333e7ec7f67ad8c_xs.jpg", "https://imagez.tmz.com/image/d1/16by9/2025/11/19/d154454483d14293b9da0a967f66c805_xs.jpg", "https://static.tmz.com/tmz-web/img/article/google-preferred-source.png", "https://imagez.tmz.com/image/28/16by9/2025/11/19/281897dd8fc94f789e10d8ee5f6498cb_xs.jpg", "https://imagez.tmz.com/image/ff/16by9/2025/11/19/fffa59b411c94fc6868ff264a08c1b45_xs.jpg"], "top_img": "https://imagez.tmz.com/image/56/16by9/2017/06/20/567a7aa968935d9fbdff35b88fd3510a_xl.jpg", "keywords": [], "authors": [], "canonical_link": "https://www.tmz.com/2017/06/20/daniel-day-lewis-quits-acting/", "title": "Daniel Day-Lewis Quits Acting",